tpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-5y4","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":11882,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/29\/umar-catch-drinking-party-spy\/","url_meta":{"origin":21332,"position":0},"title":"Umar on Spying: Umar catches drinking party, lets them go","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman ibn Awf reported: He would patrol the city at night with Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, and on one occasion they were walking when the lamp of a household caught their attention. They approached it until they heard loud voices inside the door. Umar\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33889,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/07\/umar-talaq-triple-divorce\/","url_meta":{"origin":21332,"position":1},"title":"Umar on Talaq: The Caliph punishes men who triple divorce","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 7, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: Whenever a man was brought to Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, who had divorced his wife three times in one sitting, he would flog his back. Source: Sharh\u0323 Ma\u02bba\u0304ni\u0304 al-\u0100tha\u0304r 4488 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6640,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/18\/umar-hudud-suspended-famine\/","url_meta":{"origin":21332,"position":2},"title":"Umar on Hudud: Punishment of theft suspended during famine","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Yahya ibn Abi Kathir reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThe hand of the thief is not cut who steals a bundle of dates or in a year of famine.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Abd al-Razza\u0304q 18371 Al-Sa\u2019di reported: I asked Ahmad ibn Hanbal, may Allah have\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40382,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/06\/05\/umar-faris-rum\/","url_meta":{"origin":21332,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Wealth: Umar asks for the riches of Persia and Rome","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, call upon Allah to send abundance upon your nation, for the Persians and Romans enjoy abundance and have been given the world, yet they do not worship Allah as they recline on their couches!\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18503,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.